"EOC", "type_line": "Instant", "rarity": "common", "colors": ["U"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/8/b/8b817b17-27cf-4f6b-baf2-4c4dbb3e71d1.jpg?1782685666", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/8/b/8b817b17-27cf-4f6b-baf2-4c4dbb3e71d1.jpg?1782685666", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/eoc/73/experimental-augury?utm_source=api", "local": "img/augur/2ee08dcd-5558-45be-b619-8a550f3865ad.jpg"}, {"id": "b3052531-f7cf-44a7-9492-eb155d75268c", "name": "Llanowar Augur", "set": "FUT", "type_line": "Creature — Elf Shaman", "rarity": "common", "colors": ["G"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/1/c/1c8c9473-97f4-4875-8f06-d3a70d4cbe6d.jpg?1782716666", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/1/c/1c8c9473-97f4-4875-8f06-d3a70d4cbe6d.jpg?1782716666", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/fut/129/llanowar-augur?utm_source=api", "local": "img/augur/b3052531-f7cf-44a7-9492-eb155d75268c.jpg"}, {"id": "fff28b30-9903-4a0a-a723-31216abd457d", "name": "Young Blue Dragon // Sand Augury", "set": "CLB", "type_line": "Creature — Dragon // Sorcery — Adventure", "rarity": "common", "colors": ["U"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/5/6/56b0f66b-dca9-4a01-9394-20a513c2b225.jpg?1782701283", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/5/6/56b0f66b-dca9-4a01-9394-20a513c2b225.jpg?1782701283", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/clb/106/young-blue-dragon-sand-augury?utm_source=api", "local": "img/augur/fff28b30-9903-4a0a-a723-31216abd457d.jpg"}], "flavor_snippets": [{"card": "Steel Sabotage", "set": "2XM", "html": "&quot;You are hopelessly obsolete, my brothers. Come and join the Great Work.&quot;\n—Rhmir, Hand of the <mark>Augur</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/c/2/c227437d-1fc7-4a00-ace5-80795adc51d3.jpg?1782744005"}, {"card": "Distant Memories", "set": "MBS", "html": "&quot;The fleeting shadows of his primitive self have all but vanished.&quot;\n—Jin-Gitaxias, Core <mark>Augur</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/5/158da0aa-8317-498b-89ed-2f84317fe256.jpg?1782715245"}, {"card": "Psychosis Crawler", "set": "MKC", "html": "&quot;If that brain can&#x27;t figure out the secret of the serum, then add more brains.&quot;\n—Rhmir, Hand of the <mark>Augur</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/d/0/d0f42a19-c180-45b1-9f4c-787cf3a4a649.jpg?1782694055"}, {"card": "Inexorable Tide", "set": "MM2", "html": "&quot;See how gratefully this world accepts our blessings.&quot;\n—Jin-Gitaxias, Core <mark>Augur</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/4/0/40441345-23ca-47e4-b349-bd13d986e41e.jpg?1782750609"}, {"card": "Culling Dais", "set": "2XM", "html": "&quot;Forswear the flesh and you will truly see.&quot;\n—Jin-Gitaxias, Core <mark>Augur</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/5/4/54dc8c2a-928d-465e-8f76-82a90cc66854.jpg?1782743876"}, {"card": "Psychic Miasma", "set": "SOM", "html": "&quot;A mind may be steeled against madness, but all battlements fall in time.&quot;\n—Jin-Gitaxias, Core <mark>Augur</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/f/d/fd9c3267-7988-416c-85a4-0e314e42ddb9.jpg?1782715325"}, {"card": "Lost Hours", "set": "FUT", "html": "&quot;Your thoughts do not interest me nearly as much as the absence thereof.&quot;\n—Gorghul, <mark>augur</mark> of skulls", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/4/d/4dfff4a8-43ae-41d4-acca-998234f9df35.jpg?1782716694"}, {"card": "Altar's Reap", "set": "CMA", "html": "&quot;Don&#x27;t worry, your death will be as informative as possible.&quot;\n—Gorghul, <mark>augur</mark> of skulls", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/d/1db55625-25a5-46eb-9d9c-9b3ed219359f.jpg?1782710969"}, {"card": "Xenograft", "set": "NPH", "html": "&quot;I despise Vorinclex and his slobberings about &#x27;evolution.&#x27; Only I know true progress.&quot;\n—Jin-Gitaxias, Core <mark>Augur</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/f/5/f52f08e1-b234-42e4-8f1f-485a4f6edb3b.jpg?1782715171"}, {"card": "Sunshower Druid", "set": "BLB", "html": "Apprentice <mark>augurs</mark> begin their studies by predicting where the rain will fall. Even those who don&#x27;t succeed derive great joy from the process.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/7/7/7740abc5-54e1-478d-966e-0fa64e727995.jpg?1782690477"}, {"card": "Murmuration", "set": "BLC", "html": "Once the crow birdfolk realized <mark>augurs</mark> were using the shapes of their murmurations for divination, they decided to have some fun with it.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/5/6/561c9c4e-942e-40e8-b5f2-ac709a502f18.jpg?1782690296"}, {"card": "Feast of Succession", "set": "CMM", "html": "&quot;Beware the eager host.&quot;\n—Eligeth, crossroads <mark>augur</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/7/3/73f15c50-cfb2-4567-bad5-3d18a2d7d0aa.jpg?1782733199"}, {"card": "Skyshroud Condor", "set": "TMP", "html": "Condor&#x27;s flight <mark>augurs</mark> sleepless night.\n—Skyshroud proverb", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/a/7/a7d05ef5-c046-4929-b59d-988f0313a645.jpg?1782720974"}], "mechanics_snippets": [{"card": "Kinetic Augur", "set": "M21", "html": "Kinetic <mark>Augur</mark>&#x27;s power is equal to the number of instant and sorcery cards in your graveyard."}], "thumb": {"art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/4/14fc0dfb-663a-4713-902e-96dbecc404b7.jpg?1782733207", "small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/1/4/14fc0dfb-663a-4713-902e-96dbecc404b7.jpg?1782733207", "card": "Corpse Augur"}}